      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for value over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and fading paint on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it may require some minor suspension work and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
