    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in stunning, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or hiccup anywhere! It\u2019s been babied since day one and drives just as perfectly as it looks. If you\u2019ve been looking for that 'like-new' feel without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m happy to jump on a call or show it in person whenever you're ready!",
      "price": 43500.0,
