    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46), a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, delivering linear power to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is exceptional, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with recent valve clearances and rod bearing service, this vehicle retains factory-spec compression and suspension kinematics. A true turn-key enthusiast piece with a documented service pedigree and flawless mechanical tolerances.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
