    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so the interior is spotless and the paint is just glowing. It drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, you've found it! Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
