    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This collector-grade example utilizes the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable differential lock. The vehicle is in exemplary mechanical state: the VANOS system has been comprehensively serviced, rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing fatigue. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
